If you are looking for a decent room, in a good location, for a reasonable price in New York City, don't hesitate to book here.	Didn't spend vast amount of time in the room - it is NYC afterall, however, when we did, it was a comfortable experience and certainly less expensive than the alternative, 2 hotel room option!!!	We would deffinately stay here again, everyone was very nice and the location was worth it for what we got in our room just for being a little outside of Times Square.	I would certainly be interested in staying here for a longer stay, but what's the deal with reduced cost request getting a Yes or a No?